OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,F"Car crash failures" led to the
OL,7,Ffelling of 40 palm trees at a historic
OL,8,Fseafront garden in Devon, a report has
OL,9,Ffound.
OL,11,FThe report concluded that issues with
OL,12,F"control and communication" led to a
OL,13,F"debacle" around the felling of the
OL,14,Ftrees on Torquay seafront.
OL,16,FThere was a national outcry in
OL,17,FDecember last year.
