OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,FThe palms stood in the Italian
OL,7,Fgardens, which look out over Torre
OL,8,FAbbey Sands, and had been a popular
OL,9,Ffeature since they were first planted
OL,10,Fin 1924.
OL,12,FThe gardens are one of the reasons the
OL,13,Farea is known as the English Riviera.
OL,15,FAt the time, Torbay Council said they
OL,16,F"showed significant signs of decline"
OL,17,Fand council contractors were restoring
OL,18,Fthe gardens ahead of its 100th
OL,19,Fanniversary.
