OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,FTorbay Council previously held a
OL,7,Fconsultation on the plans to cut the
OL,8,Ftrees down in 2019, but Covid meant
OL,9,Fthe plans were delayed.
OL,11,FThe report found the trees were cut
OL,12,Fdown with little or no consultation,
OL,13,Fand without council officers being
OL,14,Fmade aware it was going to happen.
OL,16,F"It was a disaster," said Torbay
OL,17,FCouncil's independent group leader
OL,18,FDarren Cowell (Shiphay).
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@TO]
