OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,F"We managed to make what should have
OL,7,Fbeen a positive story into a car
OL,8,Fcrash," he added.
OL,10,FMembers of the council's overview and
OL,11,Fscrutiny committee have examined a
OL,12,Fdetailed report into how the trees
OL,13,Fcame to be suddenly felled.
OL,15,FCouncillors have now voted to
OL,16,Fintroduce a package of measures
OL,17,Fdesigned to make sure nothing like it
OL,18,Fever happens again.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@GO]
