OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,FThe trees were felled by the council's
OL,7,Fown parks and gardens company SWISCo.
OL,8,FThe project has now been completed and
OL,9,Fthe new gardens have been well-
OL,10,Freceived, but the council and SWISCo
OL,11,Fare still feeling the effects of the
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,FMr Denby said a "failure of control"
OL,15,Fby officers had led to the felling of
OL,16,Fthe trees.
OL,18,F"It is impossible to conclude that it
OL,19,Fwas anything other than a system
OL,20,Ffailure from an officer perspective,"
OL,21,Fhe added.
OL,26,@vD@QOUvD@dO]zD@AOU
