OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,F"It is clear that the process was not
OL,7,Fwhat it should have been, and it has
OL,8,Fdamaged confidence in officers. We
OL,9,Fhave let ourselves down."
OL,11,FThe committee heard about a 200-page
OL,12,Femail trail at the heart of Mr Denby's
OL,13,Finvestigation, but they decided not to
OL,14,Fbring it to the meeting, which would
OL,15,Fhave meant excluding the press and
OL,16,Fpublic to avoid identifying the
OL,17,Findividuals involved.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]
