OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,F"What happened was awful," said Cllr
OL,7,FMartin Brook (Con, Collaton St Mary).
OL,8,F"It puts the council in a bad light
OL,9,Fand undermines the confidence for
OL,10,Fresidents. There was a stirring up of
OL,11,Fanger."
OL,13,FSWISCo managing director Matt Reeks
OL,14,Ftold the meeting the trees had been in
OL,15,Fa poor condition and were cut down
OL,16,Fafter careful consideration.
OL,18,FCllr Yvonne Twelves (Con, Kings Ash)
OL,19,Fsaid the council had to move on from
OL,20,Fthe incident.
