OL,3,C'Car crash' failures around felling of
OL,4,Cpalm trees at historic seafront gardens
OL,6,F"Finger-pointing and blame culture are
OL,7,Fnot helpful," she said. "We have to
OL,8,Fpark that, learn the lessons and move
OL,9,Fforward. Our residents want to know
OL,10,Fthat it is not going to happen again."
OL,12,FCllr Adam Billings (Con, Churston with
OL,13,FGalmpton), cabinet member for pride in
OL,14,Fplace, said: "It wasn't a case of 'who
OL,15,Fdropped the ball' but that we all
OL,16,Fdropped the ball. This is a systems
OL,17,Ffailure."
